title: Big rig overturns onto car on 405 Freeway in O.C., injuring 1 and snarling traffic
dc:creator: Gregory Yee
description: Traffic on the 405 Freeway in Seal Beach was disrupted for hours Friday afternoon after a tractor-trailer overturned onto a vehicle.
content:encoded: Traffic on the 405 Freeway in Seal Beach was disrupted for hours Friday afternoon after a tractor-trailer overturned onto a vehicle.

media:content.media:description: A tractor-trailer overturned onto a vehicle on the southbound 405 Freeway at Seal Beach Boulevard Friday afternoon.
